{"type":"tool_result","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:29:05.902Z","tool_id":"run_shell_command_1777685345779_0","status":"success","output":"commit fdb2b1fa92db98007e029e321907725f13862600 (HEAD -> feat/graceful-degradation)\nAuthor: Anthony Ainsworth <anthony@cascadiantech.com>\nDate:   Fri May 1 18:27:54 2026 -0700\n\n    feat(narrative-api): activate systemd unit on cypherclaw [T-004@20260502T001347Zc]\n    \n    Add minimal __main__ entry so 'python -m cypherclaw.narrative_api' boots\n    the FastAPI app via uvicorn (host/port/auth from env). Move\n    StartLimitIntervalSec/Burst from [Service] to [Unit] to silence the\n    systemd 'Unknown key' warning. Captures fresh evidence showing the unit\n    active, enabled, listening on Tailscale 100.74.35.114:8765, with\n    Linger=yes.\n\n my-claw/systemd/cypherclaw-narrative-api.service   |   4 +-\n ...t-004@20260502t001347zc-narrative-api-status.md | 175 +++++++++++++--------\n src/cypherclaw/narrative_api/__main__.py           |  30 ++++\n tests/test_narrative_api_main.py                   |  56 +++++++\n 4 files changed, 196 insertions(+), 69 deletions(-)\n\"\"\"Entry point so ``python -m cypherclaw.narrative_api`` boots the API.\"\"\"\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport os\n\nimport uvicorn\n\nfrom .app import create_app\n\n\ndef _resolve_host() -> str:\n    return os.environ.get(\"NARRATIVE_BIND_HOST\", \"127.0.0.1\")\n\n\ndef _resolve_port() -> int:\n    return int(os.environ.get(\"NARRATIVE_BIND_PORT\", \"8765\"))\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    app = create_app(auth_token=os.environ.get(\"NARRATIVE_AUTH_TOKEN\") or None)\n    uvicorn.run(\n        app,\n        host=_resolve_host(),\n        port=_resolve_port(),\n        log_level=os.environ.get(\"NARRATIVE_LOG_LEVEL\", \"info\"),\n    )\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()"}
